metadata.name: Personality goes a long way
metadata.description:
This is an original form of digital art. The algorithm I used to create these images is new and produces a fresh and modern aesthetic. I forgot a long time ago if Iâ€™m a programmer who learned how to make art, or an artist who learned how to code. In a way, I do exactly what every artist does, copy from reality. But I designed my own brush; I created the process to express myself. All these photos were processed with a special application I designed and programmed. The technique used is called ASCII art, but with the help of new code libraries I took it to the next level. The resulting images are more pictorial than previous text art works.
Learn more www.eldiletante.com/app
